<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="548" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="23.[811,1455,841,918]" pageId="23" pageNumber="548">
DIAGNOSIS. — Test large, subspherical to ovoid and planispiral. Wall is four-layered. 
<collectingRegion box="[965,1018,868,892]" country="Spain" name="Ceuta" pageId="23" pageNumber="548">Septa</collectingRegion>
slightly folded. Chomata massive, spherical to subquadrate in shape.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
